{"tid":804503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［昂山素姬好波］路透社兩記者查羅興亞人被殺　違緬甸機密法罪成囚7年","createTime":"2018-09-03T05:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T11:17:56.000Z","uid":6497,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6f06022f99b4e01773d9757a96cba91c9a9ee156","tid":804503,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"在緬甸調查若開邦被指屠殺羅興亞人情況的兩名路透社記者，被緬甸當局控告違反國家機密法罪成，仰光法院判處兩人監禁7年。聯合國人員要求立即釋放兩人。<br />\n<br />\n32歲的瓦倫（Wa Lone）與28歲的吳覺梭（Kyaw Soe Oo）是路透社記者，去年12月被緬甸當局以「非法獲取資訊與外國傳媒分享」為由拘捕，兩人當時正調查10名羅興亞人在若開邦印丁村遭屠殺一事。他們遭緬甸當局扣押近8個月，法院舉行了多場預審，兩人稱是遭警方設計陷害，否認控罪。案件原定上周一(8月27日)裁決，但法官因病未能開庭，延至今日宣判。<br />\n<br />\n法院判決一出，瓦倫堅持與吳覺梭皆是無辜，「我們沒有做錯事，也不對裁決感意外」。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國緬甸協調員奧斯比（Knut Ostby）要求當局立即釋放兩人，「他們應該與家人在一起及繼續新聞從業員的工作，我們會繼續呼籲爭取兩人獲釋。」<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/美國有線新聞網絡）"},{"pid":"6a91deb848c24299529f5ded6fd2bf63a3bfbfd5","tid":804503,"uid":78349,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"臭雞<br />\n昂山臭雞"},{"pid":"dcd8eaf4b7ba31980237a9d04a5d7adbb3cbe049","tid":804503,"uid":9230,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"完全係燈仔嘅夢想<br />\n<br />\n打倒獨裁因我我想做獨裁果個"},{"pid":"5458113b37b94f549bfce23b7279654bfeb4e069","tid":804503,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56c78593799f6d66dcb9498854aa78872f350e2d","tid":804503,"uid":4493,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"左膠慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67880075ccc52caee5d2a401f8691fa3f4e995b","tid":804503,"uid":20241,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"56c78593799f6d66dcb9498854aa78872f350e2d","tid":804503,"uid":4493,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"左膠慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲左膠坐多幾年先識醒"},{"pid":"2f0587b08bed474e531201ab2719c1304726311a","tid":804503,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"犯左法唔應該坐監？"},{"pid":"1e5607e2e24f6b065c1d2d97028c754c9cbe99d9","tid":804503,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"唔奇怪<br />\n<br />\n二次大戰時昂山老豆勾結日本人對抗盟軍"},{"pid":"5e133356bfcd970b635d156b61c58292eddf8d69","tid":804503,"uid":42820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:13:17.000Z","msg":"班左膠推動文明世界接收羅興亞人好過啦<br />\n好似之前接收中東佬咁<br />\n昂山而家擺明係趕絕呢班非我族類"},{"pid":"7eb2feee67ac5410540bce7833ed46b4e8de75c7","tid":804503,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcd8eaf4b7ba31980237a9d04a5d7adbb3cbe049","tid":804503,"uid":9230,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"完全係燈仔嘅夢想<br />\n<br />\n打倒獨裁因我我想做獨裁果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"有啲人種真喺唔可以比權力佢。"},{"pid":"0de25b01b168d9876364d42b4c8b124cc430f0d3","tid":804503,"uid":127988,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"人地學歐美咁反移民，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49d070a70a38a21face2e528c0970d6b0ffe47b","tid":804503,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dcd8eaf4b7ba31980237a9d04a5d7adbb3cbe049","tid":804503,"uid":9230,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"完全係燈仔嘅夢想<br />\n<br />\n打倒獨裁因我我想做獨裁果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"好驚將來會俾港獨清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd90b334b469d1186f7654351568a1dc9333569","tid":804503,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"殺回教徒係好事，啲麻煩左膠係要煽情，抵坐啦"},{"pid"